high_descs: Turn to the right, then turn to the left when you reach the sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn right, then turn left when you get to the counter with the knife on it.
Place the fork in the copper bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn left, then turn right when you get to the sink.
Place the bowl in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a fork in it in a sink.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the fork that is in the sink basin.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn left to face the end of the counter.
Put the fork into the orange bowl on the counter.
Pick up the orange bowl with the fork in it.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the orange bowl with the fork in it into the sink basin on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place an orange bowl with a fork in it into the sink basin.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink.
Grab a fork out of the sink.
Walk to the edge of the kitchen table.
Place the fork inside the orange cup.
Grab the orange cup with the fork in it.
Walk back to the kitchen sink.
Place the cup and fork inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a fork in a cup to take it back to the sink.
